    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 powerplant. This naturally aspirated unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to produce a linear power band peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis retains its precision with functional Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Recent service includes throttle actuator replacement and a rod bearing health check. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and light patina reflecting its 'good' status, the drivetrain remains robust and free of fluid leaks. A true driver's spec for those prioritizing analog feedback and atmospheric induction.",
      "price": 34500.0,
